    <name>upoints</name>
    <shortname>upoints</shortname>

    <shortdesc xml:lang="en">
        Modules for working with points on Earth
    </shortdesc>
    <description xml:lang="en">
        upoints is a collection of GPL v3 licensed modules for working with
        points on Earth, or other near spherical objects.  It allows you to
        calculate the distance and bearings between points, mangle
        xearth/xplanet data files, work with online UK trigpoint databases,
        NOAA's weather station database and other such location databases.

        Previous versions of upoints were called earth_distance, but the name
        was changed as it no longer reflected the majority of uses the packages
        was targeted at.
    </description>

